nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Ultimate Sticker Collection
Star Wars: The Clone Wars Ultimate Sticker Collection is a children's sticker book that was released on February 16, 2009.

Featuring everyone's favorite villains and heroes, as well as the coolest weapons and spaceships, burgeoning Jedi can recreate their favorite scenes from the Wars, or create new ones with the 600 stickers featured in Star Wars®: The Clone Wars Ultimate Sticker Collection.
